ZH: 公使是一位外交官的头衔。
EN: A minister is the title of a diplomat.

ZH: 他被委任为该国驻外公使。
EN: He was appointed as the country's ambassador abroad.

ZH: 这位公使需要协调两国之间的关系。
EN: The ambassador needs to coordinate the relations between two countries.

ZH: 我们的公使将在明天抵达目的地。
EN: Our ambassador will arrive at the destination tomorrow.

ZH: 我将参加公使的欢迎晚宴。
EN: I will attend the ambassador's welcome dinner.

ZH: 公使将代表我们国家在会议上发表讲话。
EN: The ambassador will speak on behalf of our country at the conference.

ZH: 公使要经常会见各国高级官员。
EN: Ambassadors often meet with senior officials from different countries.

ZH: 我们的公使在国外居住已经超过五年了。
EN: Our ambassador has been living abroad for over five years.

ZH: 在外交场合，公使享有特权和豁免权。
EN: Ambassadors enjoy privileges and immunities in diplomatic circles.

ZH: 请给公使安排一间高级套房。
EN: Please arrange a deluxe suite for the ambassador.

ZH: 我们的公使维护了两国之间的友好关系。
EN: Our ambassador maintains friendly relations between the two countries.

ZH: 公使担任了该国政府的特别使命。
EN: The ambassador undertook a special mission for the government.

ZH: 公使在外交场合代表国家并签署文件。
EN: Ambassadors represent their countries in diplomatic occasions and sign documents.

ZH: 公使提出了加强两国经济合作的建议。
EN: The ambassador proposed strengthening economic cooperation between the two countries.

ZH: 我们的公使在国内被授予了勋章。
EN: Our ambassador was awarded a medal in their home country.

ZH: 公使需要了解目标国家的政治、经济和文化情况。
EN: Ambassadors need to have an understanding of the political, economic, and cultural situations in the target country.

ZH: 这位公使与目标国家的外交官保持了密切的联系。
EN: This ambassador maintains close contact with diplomats from the target country.

ZH: 公使的职务是举行外交活动和促进两国之间的友好关系。
EN: The ambassador's duty is to carry out diplomatic activities and promote friendly relations between the two countries.

ZH: 公使出席了一个重要的国际会议。
EN: The ambassador attended an important international conference.

ZH: 公使在外交团队中负责处理与目标国家的事务。
EN: The ambassador is responsible for dealing with affairs related to the target country within the diplomatic team.
